task.summary: This is the initial commit since ersion control was not being used before. Known issues: The quit option sometimes quits even when cancel is selected.
Changed look and feel to be constant across platforms.
Fixed the problem with canceling a close still closing.
Added ability to right-click to set blank tiles on board.
Fixed a problem with blank letters not properly being accounted for when prepending to words.
